data.name: Hello World [Insane].
data.description:
This is an impossible version of Hello World!
We have all seen simple hello world , The multi line hello world's and some really amazing hello world programs. I was bored and decided to create my own version of it. It is quite simple you have a function called `_` that should return `Hello World!`. Simple isn't it. Well it has some horrible plot twists. 
All horrible plot twists

JS only : 
1). You are not allowed to use any letters other than func and these are also allowed only 
    for function declaration
2). You are not allowed to use any numbers
3). You are not allowed to use eval , Function.
4). You are not allowed to use Math object or any other for that matter
5). You are not allowed to use anything other than the following
  [] , + , - , ( , ) , !
P.S No comma (,) allowed as well
6). Also you are not allowed to have more than 3 lines in your program. (It should not take more than 2 anyway)
Well then go ahead. It is not impossible
